## üõ† Tech Stack

* ASP.NET Core Web API
* .NET 8+
* Swagger (Swashbuckle)
* Minimal middleware-based architecture

---

## üìå Design Notes

* Intentionally avoids database complexity to focus on API design
* Follows RESTful conventions and HTTP standards
* Built incrementally with non-breaking enhancements

---

## üìà Portfolio Value

This project demonstrates:

* Clean controller design
* Middleware usage
* API evolution without breaking changes
* Real-world HTTP patterns
* Production-minded thinking

